Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:23.94,Amulet_Seller,,0,0,0,,May I help you, traveller?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:28.95,Amulet_Seller,,0,0,0,,Something drew you to my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:30.95,Amulet_Seller,,0,0,0,,Something powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:36.16,Amulet_Seller,,0,0,0,,Ah, you have a keen eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:39.56,Amulet_Seller,,0,0,0,,The Alicorn Amulet is one of the most mysterious
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:43.86,Amulet_Seller,,0,0,0,,and powerful of all the known magical charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:48.38,Amulet_Seller,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid this is far too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:53.70,Amulet_Seller,,0,0,0,,Would you like that gift-wrapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:39.52,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Don't be scared, little friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:41.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Twilight is wonderful with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:46.28,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Anything happens to them, Twilight, so help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:48.59,Spike,,0,0,0,,Don't worry Fluttershy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:50.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight's magic has gotten a lot better since she accidentally
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:53.53,Spike,,0,0,0,,crushed me and Applejack with a giant snowball.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:56.51,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Of course she's good with magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.10,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Twilight's great with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.34,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I guess I just don't want my little friends to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:02.79,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, look how scared they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:07.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I promise, Fluttershy, nothing bad will happen to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.36,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.78,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,STOP! STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:17.78,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,They can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight! That looks amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:39.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's all for now, little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can practice again later,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:43.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,if Fluttershy says it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:48.25,Spike,,0,0,0,,Your magic has really improved since we came to Ponyville, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.08,Spike,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia's going to love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:50.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:54.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have to be at my best when she arrives with the delegates from Saddle Arabia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:57.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she's trusting me with the entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:01.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Come quick! It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:12.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This shade of brown should only be used for accents!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.45,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Come on, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.51,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We've got to get her into a nice, soothing pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:17.31,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Stat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:20.82,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.46,Trixie,,0,0,0,,If it isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.09,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:28.93,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:31.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You call that great and powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:40.39,Snips,,0,0,0,,Oh! She's Rainbow Wobble, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.82,Snails,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.68,Snails,,0,0,0,,Good spell, oh Great and Powerful Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.68,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You two! Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:54.33,Snips,,0,0,0,,Uh, hey! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.21,Snails,,0,0,0,,Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:03:58.75,Snips,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.21,Snails,,0,0,0,,Go this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Stop picking on my friends, Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:07.45,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You and I have some unfinished business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:10.83,Trixie,,0,0,0,,My magic's gotten better since I was here last.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:12.50,Trixie,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.68,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Me and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:15.31,Trixie,,0,0,0,,A magic duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:19.98,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Winner stays, loser leaves Ponyville forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:21.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'd never make a deal like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.76,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Hm, your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Trixie, put him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.94,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Why? Because you humiliated me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:46.33,Trixie,,0,0,0,,After you showed me up with that Ursa Minor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.44,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I became a laughing stock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:52.33,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Everywhere I went I was laughed at and ostracized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:58.18,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I even had to take a job on a rock farm just to earn a living!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:00.18,Trixie,,0,0,0,,A ROCK FARM!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:03.78,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're lucky a rock farm would take the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:13.01,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Now I want revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.62,Trixie,,0,0,0,,And I'll just keep casting spells 'til you agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:23.73,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Well? What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:27.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,Help... me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:28.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Alright, Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let's duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.55,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:44.16,Trixie,,0,0,0,,If I lose, I won't set hoof in Ponyville again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:48.37,Trixie,,0,0,0,,but if you lose, you're the one banished from this one-horse town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.33,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.23,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Snips, Snails, step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:46.33,Snails,,0,0,0,,What is it, oh The Great and Powerful Trixie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:58.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,An age spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But… how could you do an age spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:04.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's only for the highest level unicrons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:06.30,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Well, Twilight, give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:30.58,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Trixie is the highest level unicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:37.84,Trixie,,0,0,0,,And now it's time for you to leave Ponyville…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:39.84,Trixie,,0,0,0,,FOREVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:42.33,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:46.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You proved your point, but you can't possibly expect Twilight to leave Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.52,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You, fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:50.52,Trixie,,0,0,0,,She's already gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's ok, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:10.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'll figure something out. Just… take care of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:14.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And keep an eye on Trixie. There's something strange about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:16.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How could Trixie know such advanced magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:38.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Without Spike I can't get a message to the Princess in Saddle Arabia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:42.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So who else do I know who understands strange and powerful magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:49.60,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Your tale of woe upsets me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:53.23,Zecora,,0,0,0,,No wonder you dower, it's an abuse of power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:57.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do, Zecora, I feel like I've abandoned my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:59.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I can't take her on horn-to-horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.56,Zecora,,0,0,0,,If you train with me, so good you'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:06.19,Zecora,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the way, to make sure she won't stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:08.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You'll train me in magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:12.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But she was doing age spells, weather spells, you name it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:16.23,Zecora,,0,0,0,,When it comes to magic, it would be tragic, if somepony licked me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.07,Zecora,,0,0,0,,especially Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You really think I can beat her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:23.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Ok, when do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.11,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You two! Hurry up with my throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:37.06,Trixie,,0,0,0,,And you! How long do I have to wait for my applesauce facial?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:38.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Forget it, Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:42.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I ain't doing nothing 'till you let Twilight come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.92,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Ok, ok, I'll do it, just… make it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.73,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:04.77,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Trixie's cruel magic is ruining Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:11.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,No! Somepony has to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:23.60,Zecora,,0,0,0,,No noise. No sound. No din. No fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.55,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Must interfere with your focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:28.29,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Unlearn what you've learned,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:31.38,Zecora,,0,0,0,,only then can victory be earned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:36.25,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Trixie IS the higest level unicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.36,Zecora,,0,0,0,,There's much, much that I can teach,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:47.73,Zecora,,0,0,0,,but the answer you need may still be out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:51.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm trying my best, but
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't stop thinking about Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's something different about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's like she's going from high and mighty to mean and nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:01.52,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Your thinking needs a readjust,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:04.21,Zecora,,0,0,0,,total concentration is a must.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:21.20,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This really doesn't seem to be getting us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.32,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Ah hear you, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:29.73,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I can't find anything that describes a kind of magic Trixie's doin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,There must be something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight has every magic book there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.11,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I think I may have found something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:41.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It's time for us to consider our future in this new Trixie-led Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:44.08,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Thats sounds an awful lot like Trixie's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She wants me to grow apples with no peels!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:48.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now how the hay am Ah supposed to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:51.93,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,There's a picture here of that necklace…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:57.08,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's called the Alicorn Amulet and whoever wears it is blessed with untold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.32,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hey, everypony, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,This book has a picture of Trixie's necklace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,it's called the Alicorn Amulet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:05.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,and whoever wears it is blessed with untold powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:07.70,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,If you read a little further you will see…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:09.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Even though it provides the great power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,it also corrupts the user!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.64,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Yes, but... Ehm, you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:15.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,You can't just take the Alicorn Amulet off her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,It has the magical lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Trixie is the only pony who can take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:20.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.87,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We need to get this information to Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:23.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She will know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:24.83,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But. How...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:28.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,If any of us try to leave, Trixie's magical forcefield will tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:29.96,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:30.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:34.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Trying to sneak past the forcefield would be impossible without help,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:37.82,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,but I know who's got the goods to get into those woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.34,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:39.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:39.90,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,WHAAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:42.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:44.11,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Can you handle the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:47.51,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,No! I'll crack under the pressure! I'll snap like a twig!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:51.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Perfect! Fluttershy will sneak out of Ponyville and find Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.52,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But. But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:01.44,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.03,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,All right go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:08.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And I know just the design for a dangerous mission outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.79,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Pull, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:22.36,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Somepony set up the magic forcefield and Trixie intends to punish them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:26.56,Snips,,0,0,0,,But... wouldn't it be faster if we had some wheels?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:29.29,Trixie,,0,0,0,,The Great and Powerful Trixie doesn't trust wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:30.56,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Now pull faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.74,Snails,,0,0,0,,I'm telling ya, Snips.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.64,Snails,,0,0,0,,She's getting weirder and weirder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:40.86,Trixie,,0,0,0,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.58,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You there! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:03.20,Snails,,0,0,0,,Why is she so mean to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:06.11,Snips,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I miss the days when she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.74,Snips,,0,0,0,,just a fraud!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.97,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh dear! Rarity's dangerous mission outfit is ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:24.53,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Guess we'd better go back. Ha-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.07,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Okay-okay, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:31.34,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I need to be brave and find Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.92,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.70,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,She's in the Everfree Forest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:41.59,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,This is me being brave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:44.96,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I wanna be brave at home! Locked in my closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.00,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,With my teddy bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:54.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I didn't recognise the Alicorn Amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:57.81,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,The more she uses it, the more it will corrupt her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:00.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But how am I supposed to beat that amulet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My magic's not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:04.40,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle, much work have you done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:08.05,Zecora,,0,0,0,,You've learned all of my lessons. All, but one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:11.39,Zecora,,0,0,0,,If Trixie's tricks have you in a fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:15.31,Zecora,,0,0,0,,You must mix your magic and use the six.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fix your magic… Use the six…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:20.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fix your magic, use the six!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:21.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Use the six, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Zecora, you're genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:28.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Now we need to get you back inside Ponyville, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:43.32,Trixie,,0,0,0,,This better not to be another false alarm, or The Great and Powerful Trixie will…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.82,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:49.92,Trixie,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Twilight Sparkle? Not enjoing your exile?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:53.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,, I know about the Alicorn Amulet. I know you cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:54.66,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Cheated?..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:16:00.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I thought you might wanna see what a real magical amulet looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:01.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Zecora gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's from beyond the Everfree Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:07.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And it's way more powerful than your measly little Alicorn Amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:11.14,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Nothing's more powerful than the alicorn's amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:16.62,Trixie,,0,0,0,,And nopony is more powerful than the Great and Powerful Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:20.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Care to put your amulet to where your mouth is? How about another duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.88,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Why should I? I already beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:29.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's up to you, but I guess you'll never see the totally awesome magic from beyond the Everfree Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:32.90,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.01,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Ok, ok, you're on. A second duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:53.85,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Let's start with a simple age spell, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:54.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.16,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Snips, Snails!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:09.01,Trixie,,0,0,0,,An oldie but a goodie. Now, let's see what your little charm can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.14,Trixie,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:14.69,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Applejack, Rarity, could you help me please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:36.84,Trixie,,0,0,0,,So you can do an age spell, big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:53.65,Trixie,,0,0,0,,That's… That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:08.20,Trixie,,0,0,0,,How did you?…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:09.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Duplication spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:12.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Ever seen one pony play ten instruments?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:24.58,Trixie,,0,0,0,,This… just can't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:28.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,One more! I can turn a mare into a stallion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:42.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, Trixie, looks like my amulet is more powerful than yours…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:44.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hey! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:52.41,Trixie,,0,0,0,,With this amulet, I shall now rule all of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:00.35,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Witness, my subjects!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:05.77,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Gaze upon the ever Greater and Powerfuler Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.58,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I don't need that old Alicorn Amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.68,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:23.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Stop it! That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.83,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Tickles? That was supposed to make you ride in agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:30.95,Trixie,,0,0,0,,This amulet is defected. Give mine back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:34.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sorry. This is going back into hiding where it belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:39.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,By the way, Trixie, the amulet around your neck — it's one of Zecora's doorstops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:45.92,Trixie,,0,0,0,,But… How did you do those spells? Nopony can do those spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:48.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're right! Not even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:52.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Zecora taught me so much about magic while I was in exile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:54.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She even taught me when not to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:20:01.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My magic alone wasn't powerful enough to take on the Alicorn Amulet head to head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:03.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So I needed to use a different kind of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:06.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The magic of friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:10.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I also knew that the only pony who could get the amulet off your neck was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:14.77,Trixie,,0,0,0,,But what about the pony with the ten instruments?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:17.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's not magic, that was just Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:48.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Trixie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.88,Trixie,,0,0,0,,It's the least I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:55.34,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I treated you and your friends so horribly when I was wearing that Alicorn Amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:58.00,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't controll myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:21:00.88,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You can forgive me, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:05.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:08.07,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:14.62,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Don't you think the Great and Apologetic Trixie is the most magnificient humble pony you've ever seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.05,Somepony,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVYI PONETC
